  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Enjoy a buffet breakfast each morning in the bright dining room or outside on the terrace where you'll have views of the garden and pool. You'll have various options including fresh pastries, cereal, fruit, jams, yoghurt, cheeses, cold cuts and scrambled eggs. To drink you'll have a choice of coffee, teas and fruit juices.</p>
<p><strong>Restaurant 1910</strong> is the hotels à la carte restaurant and is open for dinner (bookable &amp; payable locally). </p>
<p><strong>Liberty Cafè &amp; Bar</strong> opens throughout the day and is ideal for a morning coffee, light lunch or to sample some of the region's famous wines.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
