  <description><![CDATA[<p>Grand Hotel Liberty is right in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/8bac09b5ee37405a9498e1494235fa01" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8bac09b5ee37405a9498e1494235fa01}" title="Riva">Riva</a>. You couldn’t be better placed for exploring the town or taking lakeside walks. You’ll have Riva’s cafés, bars and restaurants on your doorstep.</p>
<h2>Art Nouveau style hotel near central Riva</h2>
<p>Grand Hotel Liberty has a timeless elegance – it’s Art Nouveau façade houses high, arched ceilings and a traditional décor of parquet floors and antiques. Head out back for the outdoor pool; there are loungers on the surrounding lawn so lay down your towel and top up your tan. When it’s time for dinner, the restaurant serves up traditional Italian food with a modern twist (bookable and payable locally), or head into town for a delicious Italian feast. Make sure you save lots of room!</p>]]></description>
