  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Grand Hotel Liberty is in the centre of Riva, next to the town's café and bars and close to the lake. It's an elegant hotel with an impressive décor and lovely pool in the gardens. Head to the spa when you want to relax. You'll find an indoor pool, sauna, Turkish bath and whirlpool.</p>
