  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Comfort Rooms</strong> are about 20m² and sleep two people.</p>
<p><strong>Family Comfort Rooms </strong>are about 25m² and sleep three to four people (extra bed is a double sofa bed). These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Single Comfort Rooms </strong>are about 15m². </p>
<p><strong>Comfort Rooms for sole use </strong>are also available.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Air-conditioning (mid-June to mid-September)</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Shower stall</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available on request for approx. €10 per day, payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Local fees &amp; taxes</strong></p>
<p>A tourist tax of approx. €2.50 per person per day is payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
